title: Bobby's Instagram Search For A Wedding Date + Judah & The Lion Stop By
itunes:title: Bobby's Instagram Search For A Wedding Date + Judah & The Lion Stop By
description:
Bobby has two weddings to go to this year, so he's inviting listeners interested in being his date to DM him on Instagram. Also, Judah & The Lion stop by to talk about their new song "Pictures" featuring Kacey Musgraves.
